creator: guo yun
descriptionHtml:
Aiming Expert for 8 Ball Pool is a professional tool for 8 ball pool players and helps you become a master in the billiards or pool games. It can help you aim the ball and extend the aim line automatically. Easy to make nice and accurate shots, not limited to direct straight shots but also aim bank shots or cushion shots easily.

Aiming Expert have the following features:
1. Auto lengthen guideline during game play
2. 100% Safe, No hack, with AI Image Recognition
3. Support bank shot & kick shot

Disclaimer: Aiming Expert is only applicable to 8 Ball Pool. Please use it reasonably to practice your playing skills.Hope you become a 8-ball Expert!
